<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 15:13:38 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国就军舰进入台海向加拿大提出投诉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-filed-complaints-with-canada-over-warship-taiwan-strait-2024-08-02/</link><description>中国国防部周五表示，加拿大军舰穿越台湾海峡后，中国已通过军事和外交渠道向加拿大提出投诉。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 10:58:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-filed-complaints-with-canada-over-warship-taiwan-strait-2024-08-02/</guid></item><item><title>酷热席卷华东地区，杭州、上海酷热难耐</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hangzhou-shanghai-broil-extreme-heat-engulfs-eastern-china-2024-08-02/</link><description>中国东部沿海的大城市正面临又一轮酷暑，周五气温徘徊在 40 摄氏度（104 华氏度）左右，预计下周将持续持续极端气温。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 10:33:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hangzhou-shanghai-broil-extreme-heat-engulfs-eastern-china-2024-08-02/</guid></item><item><title>跳水-男子双人3米跳板中国队王龙获得冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/diving-chinas-wang-long-win-mens-synchronised-3m-springboard-2024-08-02/</link><description>周五，中国选手王宗源和龙道一在巴黎奥运会上卫冕了中国男子双人三米跳板冠军，夺得了中国在这项运动中的第四枚金牌，并保持了包揽全部八枚金牌的目标。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 10:13:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/diving-chinas-wang-long-win-mens-synchronised-3m-springboard-2024-08-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国大学开设首个婚姻相关学位课程</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-university-announces-first-marriage-related-degree-course-2024-08-02/</link><description>中国民政大学宣布了一个新的本科婚姻课程，以发展与婚姻相关的产业和文化，此举引起了社交媒体用户的嘲笑，他们质疑在结婚率下降的情况下开设此类课程的必要性。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 08:27:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-university-announces-first-marriage-related-degree-course-2024-08-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国救援人员在致命洪水后竞相寻找失踪的密封堤坝</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/rescuers-china-race-find-missing-seal-dykes-after-devastating-floods-2024-08-02/</link><description>今年最强台风席卷湖南省一周后，中国的救援人员于周五紧急寻找数十名失踪人员，同时紧急救援人员也忙于封堵汹涌河流上决口的堤坝。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 06:25:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/rescuers-china-race-find-missing-seal-dykes-after-devastating-floods-2024-08-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行顾问呼吁加大刺激力度，实现通胀目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-central-bank-adviser-calls-greater-stimulus-inflation-goal-2024-08-02/</link><description>一位央行政策顾问在周五的讲话中表示，中国应加大财政刺激力度以刺激经济增长，并设定坚定的通胀目标，以防止国家陷入“低通胀陷阱”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 05:51:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-central-bank-adviser-calls-greater-stimulus-inflation-goal-2024-08-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国缓慢复苏令全球企业增长前景黯淡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-stuttering-recovery-darkens-global-corporate-growth-outlook-2024-08-02/</link><description>全球汉堡连锁店和汽车制造商越来越感受到世界第二大经济体中国复苏乏力的压力，并准备迎接未来的坎坷之路。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 04:18:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-stuttering-recovery-darkens-global-corporate-growth-outlook-2024-08-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国官方媒体和网民在潘基文声称“人类不可能”完成100米游泳后团结起来</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/chinas-state-media-netizens-rally-around-pan-after-claims-100m-swim-not-humanly-2024-08-02/</link><description>在包括澳大利亚游泳评论员在内的批评者称潘占乐在100米自由泳中创造世界纪录“不可能”之后，中国官方媒体、运动员和网民纷纷集会支持奥运会游泳冠军潘占乐。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 03:03:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/chinas-state-media-netizens-rally-around-pan-after-claims-100m-swim-not-humanly-2024-08-02/</guid></item><item><title>长期来看，中国需要的不仅仅是“增量”消费刺激</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-needs-more-than-incremental-consumer-stimulus-longer-term-2024-08-01/</link><description>中国刺激家庭支出的努力预计将有助于经济实现政府2024年约5%的增长目标，但当局可能必须从明年开始为消费者采取更多措施，否则就接受增长放缓。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 23:05:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-needs-more-than-incremental-consumer-stimulus-longer-term-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>来自中国的原始刺蛞蝓是世界软体动物的先驱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/science/primordial-spiny-slug-china-was-forerunner-worlds-mollusks-2024-08-01/</link><description>地球上大约有 76,000 种软体动物，其​​形态各异，包括蛤、牡蛎、扇贝、贻贝、蜗牛、蛞蝓，甚至还有一些具有非凡智力的软体动物，如章鱼、墨鱼和鱿鱼。但它们的祖先形态和早期进化历史一直难以破译。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 18:11:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/science/primordial-spiny-slug-china-was-forerunner-worlds-mollusks-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>新华社称中国政策性银行原副行长被开除党籍</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-vice-president-chinese-policy-bank-expelled-communist-party-xinhua-says-2024-08-01/</link><description>据官方通讯社新华社周四报道，国家开发银行原副行长李继平因涉嫌严重违纪违法，被开除党籍。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 09:23:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-vice-president-chinese-policy-bank-expelled-communist-party-xinhua-says-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国驳回德国有关网络攻击的指控</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/germany-made-groundless-accusations-about-china-related-cyber-threats-says-2024-08-01/</link><description>中国驻柏林大使馆周四驳斥了德国关于北京在 2021 年对德国政府机构发起网络攻击的指控，称其为毫无根据的指控，并指责其“反华政治操纵”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 07:12:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/germany-made-groundless-accusations-about-china-related-cyber-threats-says-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>对冲资金流 对中国的对冲基金配置创五年新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hedge-flow-hedge-fund-allocations-china-hit-five-year-low-2024-08-01/</link><description>高盛在给客户的一份报告中表示，全球对冲基金已将中国股票的敞口削减至五年来的最低水平，同时加大对日本的投资。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 06:54:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hedge-flow-hedge-fund-allocations-china-hit-five-year-low-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国创下近期历史上最热月份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-records-hottest-month-recent-history-2024-08-01/</link><description>据中国官方媒体报道，中国7月份经历了现代历史上最热的一个月，这与上个月世界各地出现的创纪录的炎热天气相似。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 06:39:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-records-hottest-month-recent-history-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>PMI调查增加前景风险，中国工厂准备迎接“残酷的夏天”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-contracts-first-time-9-months-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-08-01/</link><description>中国低迷的制造业即将迎来“残酷的夏天”，本周的两项信心调查显示，因需求疲软而苦苦挣扎的工厂主的悲观情绪达到了新的水平，预示着2024年下半年经济增长面临风险。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 01:52:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-contracts-first-time-9-months-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-08-01/</guid></item></channel></rss>